  "text": "Found all Java source files in apache/kafka that implement consumer group partition assignment strategies. The implementations are located in two modules:\n\nCLIENT-SIDE IMPLEMENTATIONS (in the 'clients' module for KafkaConsumer):\n\n1. AbstractPartitionAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractPartitionAssignor.java) - Base abstract class implementing ConsumerPartitionAssignor interface that provides common functionality for partition assignors.\n\n2. AbstractStickyAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractStickyAssignor.java) - Intermediate abstract base class extending AbstractPartitionAssignor that provides shared sticky assignment logic used by both StickyAssignor and CooperativeStickyAssignor.\n\n3. RangeAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RangeAssignor.java) - Assigns partitions on a per-topic basis in contiguous ranges. Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor.\n\n4. RoundRobinAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RoundRobinAssignor.java) - Assigns partitions to consumers in a round-robin fashion. Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor.\n\n5. StickyAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/StickyAssignor.java) - Guarantees balanced assignment while preserving existing partition assignments using eager rebalancing. Extends AbstractStickyAssignor.\n\n6. CooperativeStickyAssignor (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/CooperativeStickyAssignor.java) - Follows same sticky logic as StickyAssignor but supports cooperative rebalancing protocol for reduced downtime. Extends AbstractStickyAssignor.\n\nSERVER-SIDE IMPLEMENTATION (in the 'group-coordinator' module for the new group coordinator):\n\n7. RangeAssignor (group-coordinator/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/coordinator/group/assignor/RangeAssignor.java) - Server-side range assignor implementing ConsumerGroupPartitionAssignor interface for the new group coordinator protocol. Assigns contiguous partition ranges ensuring each subscribed member receives partitions and same partition numbers across topics when co-partitioning is possible.\n\nInheritance hierarchy:\n- AbstractPartitionAssignor extends ConsumerPartitionAssignor\n  - RangeAssignor (clients) extends AbstractPartitionAssignor\n  - RoundRobinAssignor extends AbstractPartitionAssignor\n  - AbstractStickyAssignor extends AbstractPartitionAssignor\n    - StickyAssignor extends AbstractStickyAssignor\n    - CooperativeStickyAssignor extends AbstractStickyAssignor\n\n- RangeAssignor (group-coordinator) implements ConsumerGroupPartitionAssignor directly (separate implementation for server-side)"
